md:name.md:partName: (Ahmad ibn al-Husayn al-Mutanabbī, d. 354 H [965 CE])

md:note.div:
Digtsamling, hvor de fleste af digte er skrevet af Ahmad ibn al-Husayn al-Mutanabbī. Resten af dem er forfattet af Ibrāhīm ibn Sahl al-Isrā'īlī al-Išbīlī (d. 649 H [1151] eller 658 H [1260].
Cod. Arac. 243

Collection of poetry. Most of the poems are written by Ahmad ibn al-Husayn al-Mutanabbī. The rest of them is written by Ibrāhīm ibn Sahl al-Isrā'īlī al-Išbīlī (d. 649 H [1151 CE] eller 658 H [1260 CE].
Cod. Arac. 243
